13
00:00:43.843 --> 00:00:46.746
Here we have it for our purposes,
we took the leg off.

14
00:00:47.113 --> 00:00:49.315
I'm going to show you the other side.

15
00:00:49.315 --> 00:00:50.683
Remove the skin, not remove

16
