right on the joint and I can feel it
moving up and down or back and forth.

20
00:01:01.561 --> 00:01:05.131
I'm going to take my French knife
and you notice my French knives are nice

21
00:01:05.131 --> 00:01:05.965
and clean.

22
00:01:05.965 --> 00:01:08.101
And I always like to have water
close to me.

23
00:01:08.435 --> 00:01:12.405
Maybe a cloth, put my knife down
wipe it properly.

24
00:01:12.605 --> 00:01:14.574
