25
00:01:14.574 --> 00:01:17.477
Hold the knife with my thumb
and my index finger

26
00:01:18.344 --> 00:01:21.448
using my non cutting hand
feel where the bone is.

27
00:01:21.781 --> 00:01:26.152
Replace my finger with the knife
and just cut right through

28
00:01:26.586 --> 00:01:30.356
so I can get that drumstick off the thigh.

29
00:01:34.661 --> 00:01:38.565
Here is
the thigh and here is the drumstick.

30
00:01:38.598 --> 00:01:41.034
I like to trim a little bit of the knuckle
right off.

31
00:01:42.669 --> 00:01:45.605
And that is the same process

32
00:01:46.973 --> 00:01:50.276
holding the knife,
getting close to the end of the knife.

33
00:01:51.478 --> 00:01:53.913
Using your non cutting hand
so you don't slip.

34
00:01:54.514 --> 00:01:57.317
Put it on top and just cut straight down.

35
00:02:00.920 --> 00:02:04.390
And now you have your drum

36
